Raquel Naa Ayorkor Ammah (a mụrụ n'abalị iri na abụọ nke ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1987) amaara aha nkwago ihe omume ya dị ka Raquel, bụ onye Ghana na-eti egwu, onye na-ede egwu, onye na-echeputa ma hazie egwu, onye na-eme ihe nkiri na onye  edemede. A maara ya nke ọma maka egwu ya bụ bu "Sweetio" nke gosipụtara Sarkodie.

A mụrụ Raquel na United Kingdom site n'ọmụmụ  nne na nna si Ghana. O tolitere na West London ya na nne ya, ụmụnne  ya nwoke abụọ na nwanne ya nwanyị. Raquel gara ọtụtụ ụlọ akwụkwọ n'ihi na ezinụlọ ya kwahariri n'ọtụtụ ụlọ ugboro ole na ole
Otú ọ dị, ụlọ akwụkwọ kachasị amasị ya ka bụ Hogarth Primary School nke dị na Chiswick, na West Thames College.

Raquel batara n'otiti egwu n'afọ 2005 ma kemgbe ahụ, ya na ndị n'eti egwu na mba ụwa dịka Mario, Movado, Young (U.S) Lloyd (U.S), Kas (Nigeria), Cabbo Snoop (Angola), Duncan Mighty (Nigeria), Stephanie Benson (UK / Ghana) na akụkọ ka egwu. O wepụtara "Odo" dị ka egwu  ya kachasịnụ n'ọnwa July 2010.

Dị ka akụkụ nke ya na ntunye ọrụ mmekọrịta mmadụ na ibe ya, Raquel ewepụtala onwe  ya  ịbụ onye ndụmọdụ maka ọrụ ebere onwe ya n'ime obodo ya n'ime Ghana nke a na-akpọ Christ Humanitarian Foundation (CHF)
Ọ na-arụ ọrụ dị ka onye na-akwado ọha na eze maka ntọala ahụ iji nyere ha aka inweta ego kwa afọ.
O ritere ihe nrite nke nwanyị nwere nka n'egwu kacha mma nke afọ 2012 bụ Best Female Artist 2012, na YFM All Star Weekend Awards, December, 2012
O nwekwara otu nhọpụta na Hip Hop na RnB Awards 2011.
